🖤ONYX🖤 ⁣ I am beyond excited to share with you all a very special project that I’ve been working on over the past year. — My very 1st Monograph!⁣
⁣
ONYX is a dream project that I photographed in Houston, TX over the course of 2020. The series embodies all things fantasy, femininity, and power – all while documenting some of the most beautiful performers at Houston’s iconic, Club Onyx.  I am endlessly inspired by sensuality and the beauty of the female form. These photographs reflect an enticing, bold visual style — all while capturing the nuances of Houston nightlife and honoring the dancers at Onyx from an empowered, artful perspective. ONYX tells a visual narrative in the heat of the moment — lending a true unstaged glimpse into the artistry and emotion present in each performers experience. ⁣
⁣
ONYX was printed and published by @Damiani_books in Italy and is available worldwide. The book features 168 pages of portraits with text written by Houston’s own @itsnandibby. — Designed by the amazing @tessaforrest. 💗
⁣
Signed copies with limited edition prints are available exclusively through my website — Signed copies can also be purchased via my IG shop. ⁣
⁣
 Huge thank you and lots of love to the ladies at Club Onyx, and to everyone who has supported my work thus far! 💗🫶🏾

❤️‍🔥𝐎𝐍𝐘𝐗❤️‍🔥 In Press! 

Huge thank you to all writers and publications who have covered the book release for ONYX. ❣️
